IMPORTANT — SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE

The MIT license above applies ONLY to the restoration patches and tooling
authored as part of this repository's commit history. It does NOT cover:

  - The original UberStrike game assets (models, textures, audio, scenes,
    materials, animations, prefabs) which are © Cmune Ltd. and shipped
    publicly with the 2014 Steam release of UberStrike 4.7.1.

  - The decompiled-and-cleaned C# source code recovered from Cmune's
    Unity 4.6 Assembly-CSharp.dll and Assembly-CSharp-firstpass.dll. That
    code is © Cmune Ltd. and is included here for educational and
    preservation purposes only.

  - Third-party Unity packages declared in Packages/manifest.json, which
    are governed by their respective licenses (typically Unity Companion
    License or Unity Package Distribution License).

This repository exists for preservation and educational study of a
discontinued game. If you are a Cmune rights holder, contact the maintainer
and the repository will be taken down on request.
